    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that just sounds like the official talking points. if it was just \"complex issues\" then why does it feel so targeted? like, look at how the big banks and the people in power are getting richer while the rest of us can barely pay rent. it feels more like a deliberate squeeze to consolidate wealth and move us into a lower class. dont you think the way the Fed operates basically protects the elites while the average person gets crushed?",
